data.description: Want to be in the country but near everything? Need a fenced in backyard for pets or kids? Need 4 BRs without breaking the bank? Want an affordable home that has just been substantially renovated? THEN THIS IS THE ONE! 4 BR/2 Full Bath. New paint throughout. New Luxury Vinyl Plank. New butcher block countertop in huge eat-in kitchen (buyer can stain/seal to their preference). Fenced in backyard. Former laundry room on lower level that could easily be converted to full bath #3. Nice deck overlooking backyard just stained. Radon mitigation system in place. Deep, 2 car side-load garage. Nice country subdivision with minimal restrictions and no HOA/fees. Fireplace with gas logs in living room. One of larger floorplans in subdivision. Very close to Kernersville and Walkertown. Upper level has all living space including laundry; lower level has extra bedroom, large open den or bonus area, and former laundry room (future bath?). Great road appeal. Move-in ready to an extreme! Great floorplan!
